# Suppress duplicate C declaration warnings (rank/nRanks appear in multiple
# structs in the C API). autodoc warnings (mocked-object, import-failure)
# are intentionally NOT suppressed: they signal that a Python symbol cannot
# be introspected, which usually means a missing dependency or a broken
# install -- both worth surfacing during the build.
